response.original_title: GCW vs Renegades of Wrestling Australian Tour 2023, August 26th
response.overview: On August 26th is the second day of GCW's Australian Tour 2023 and their next stop is the Melbourne Pavilion. The first matches in the lineup are already announced and you can check them below:  Lochy Hendricks vs Effy  Four Way Match Charli Evans vs Allie Katch vs Steph De Lander  Tag Team Match Joey Janela & JXT vs The Bastard Brothers (Gore & KrackerJak)  ROW Women's Title Match Aysha (c) vs Maki Itoh  El Hijo del Vikingo vs Emman Azman  WrestleRock Title Six Way Scramble Match Jake Andrewartha (c) vs Fun Time Phil vs Murdoch vs Anth Cava vs Jarvis vs Levi Nixon  ROW Title Match Caveman Ugg (c) vs Gringo Loco
response.title: GCW vs Renegades of Wrestling Australian Tour 2023, August 26th
